    GREENWICH, Conn., March 25 - <purchaser>Clabir Corp</purchaser> and <acquired>AmBrit Corp</acquired>
said they <status>called off their plans</status> for <purchabr>Clabir</purchabr> to buy the 16 pct
voting interest in <acqabr>AmBrit</acqabr> that it does not already own.
    The companies said they agreed not to pursue the merger
because several actions recently taken by <acqabr>AmBrit</acqabr> would mean
